Personnally, I would look at items with mods first (Esp. Percu cause it sux w/o it for OoS and HoS). Then i would go for what give the more HP (Raw or from Sta). Thirdly, i would look Cha. Cha and Agi are by far the hardest stats to bring up. I wouldnt bother with Int/Dex because those 2 stats are on about every item you get for some reason. Same goes with mana, usually HP Items always have a Mana equivalent, so it will, as well just, come with it. STR/Wis are the useless stats to look for (str is because our song give like 3678 str or something 0_o).&quot;Fourthly&quot;, look for resists (Esp MR cause snare/root blow) and try to cap them with Songs on. After all this you add gravy with melee focus (Avoidance, shielding, stun resist etc..)
